"We have a role."

00:04:30.585 --> 00:04:33.141
So when I speak to these leaders, I say,

00:04:33.165 --> 00:04:37.018
"Look, you could be the CEO,
a very successful CEO of a company,

00:04:37.042 --> 00:04:39.113
but you could also be a steward."

00:04:39.669 --> 00:04:40.882
And that's the key word.

00:04:40.906 --> 00:04:44.458
"You could be a steward
of the power you have

00:04:44.482 --> 00:04:48.394
to shape the lives and the economies
of billions of people.

00:04:48.967 --> 00:04:50.551
Which one do you want to be?"

00:04:51.218 --> 00:04:53.821
